{"tid":1205303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"罷睇tvb","createTime":"2019-06-11T17:56:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T18:14:27.000Z","uid":155320,"like":29,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f4372dcd4782d0e6b7c994b94c86eb573f668383","tid":1205303,"uid":155320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:56:38.000Z","msg":"唔係罷睇咁簡單<br />\n係直頭令自己屋企電視睇唔到<br />\n雖然我唔知可以點，有人話蚊左個cable線定點<br />\n有冇咩實際方法可以令自己屋企block左tvb<br />\n<br />\n如果唔想老豆老母睇完咁多廢話，立即行動<br />\n（蚊左條線 佢地都唔撚識啦死廢老）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申屋企冇電視"},{"pid":"39c9956cd7cd0e64de066a0d6964582238bf4cc4","tid":1205303,"uid":155320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:58:16.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n有冇電視撚識？"},{"pid":"e220e17570e1e404ff7322281446b991b5922ba7","tid":1205303,"uid":258758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:58:53.000Z","msg":"借個位黎推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫手del 哂屋企長輩啲大台app<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1204207\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1204207</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e42bf8bab5168fc66aa82c7c3b100e947d2740d2","tid":1205303,"uid":258758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e220e17570e1e404ff7322281446b991b5922ba7","tid":1205303,"uid":258758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:58:53.000Z","msg":"借個位黎推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫手del 哂屋企長輩啲大台app<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1204207\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1204207</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:59:25.000Z","msg":"入面有哂教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68b77d6b6788a176d680d1054bd7084168054a4","tid":1205303,"uid":155320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:00:19.000Z","msg":"block完tvb<br />\n連佢d9戲都唔撚洗睇<br />\n<br />\n老豆老母要睇未叫佢地睇手機apps<br />